Class Memorie

  • java.lang.Object
    • subscription.Memorie

  • public class Memorie
extends java.lang.Object
    LinkedList simulation of a memory object that makes use of a cache to better respond to requests.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description

      Constructs a list representing the memory and also associates it to an already created cache type.
